âœ… 3. Start a Full Vulnerability Scan
Go to Scans > Tasks â†’ New Task

Name: Localhost Full Scan

Scan Target: Localhost

Scanner: Full and fast

Save, then click the play button â–¶ï¸ to start scan

â±ï¸ Scan Duration: 30â€“60 minutes depending on system performance

âœ… 4. Wait for the Scan to Complete
Monitor scan under Scans > Tasks

When done, status shows Done or Completed

âœ… 5. Review the Report
Go to Scans > Reports

